properties.comment: In the winter of 2010 I flew to Puerto Vallarta Mexico and camped on the beach in Sayulita for a week.
I took a bus to guadalajara mexico and stayed in a youth hostel there.
I spent a week in Aguas Calientes Mexico and made some great friends there. They even held a bbq for me in an abandoned house when I left.
I used to have to drive up to Fort Mcmurray for work to do soil survey in the boreal forest. I also was lucky enough to work on a fly in/fly out job at an ice road construction project.
My friend Alex and I drove to Prince Albert National
My 3rd grade class trip in Florida was at a marine biology camp on Big Pine Key FL. We also spent a day in Key West FL

properties.end: Buenos Aires, Autonomous City of Buenos Aires, Argentina
properties.comment: In 2004 I was luck enough to go on an exchange program in Parana Argentina. I attended a catholic boys school and stayed with a host family.
I travelled with my Argentinean host brother by bus to the city of Corrientes Argentina to visit his relatives for a week.
While in Correintes Argentina with my host brother we took a trip to visit the famous Iguazu falls on the border with Brazil.
